	* aclocal.m4: Updated syntax to autoconf 2.59.
	(GROFF_HTML_PROGRAMS): Use AC_FOREACH.
	Don't check for gsos2.
	(GROFF_SRCDIR, GROFF_BUILDDIR): Removed.  autoconf 2.59 provides
	working abs_top_srcdir and abs_top_builddir.

