2003-08-31  Werner LEMBERG  <wl@gnu.org>

	* Makefile.comm: Use `test ... ||' in favor of `if test ...; then'.
	(install_dev, uninstall_dev): Check whether $(DEVSCRIPTS) and
	$(DEVFILES) are not empty.
